reviewText: Go Fish did it again...another great cd and/or DVD (as I bought both!).  The kids love this and so do all of the leaders!  I have their whole collection in my car!  lol :)
My kids love Go fish guys.  They watched this for hours.
The kids love the music and the choreography. I love the message - and the music.
Can't go wrong with "go fish"!  Middle school kids love it at Sunday school
Awesome just as I expected. Can't wait to order more!
This was a gift, and my niece loved it.
My kids love the music and the motions and songs are great!  The only problem is, it isn't long enough.  :-)
Go Fish Guys always ROCK!  Great worship for kids.  My kids love them.
My 2 1/2 year old loves this video!!
The Go Fish Guys are great. Adults enjoy their music too.
My child went crazy over this! Loved it!
Love those Go Fish guys!  I use this video at church with Kids ministry.  The kids love it.  Most songs have lots of motions the kids can do.
